content.detailedDescription: The info came from the east and was traveling fast going southeast.I think about 1030 at night it was moving fast and no airplane like lights
content.summary: At the trailer had no airplane like lights took a video 33 seconds

content.detailedDescription: I was sitting in my backyard at 7pm, a clear blue sky, no clouds & no wind just enjoying the night. i was facing the west and just looked up in the sky when i noticed 4 contrails,smoke clouds, moving fast against the sky eastward. they were moving at the same level not like a regular airliner, too low. the 4 planes were moving side by side at the same altitude. i noticed that the jets kept pace with the silver or white discs that were front of only 3 of the jets. i ran to the front of my house which faces the east and the jets seemed to stop their pursuit. i did not hear any noises from any of the jets or the silver discs. it is the first time i have seen that many planes/jets that close together and moving at such a fast pace. i was so surprised to see this on a clear evening, a disc being chased by jets, and one plane was to that right not in the same formation, a bit off center.
content.summary: Early evening, no clouds in the sky,clear blue sky,i saw 4 white trails of planes or jets at the same level,side by side caught my attention, i saw 3 silver dots,in front of chase planes then gone

content.detailedDescription: I was outside watching the night sky, it was sprinkling a little i noticed to the west of me 2 lights, one white one blue, were stationary at first started to spin merged into one light shot st eight up into one big white light then gone. no sound no wind just gone this is the second time the lights have been here by my house
content.summary: White and blue light seperate then started circling then merged then shot st right up into a white light then gone 2nd sighting

content.detailedDescription: Triangular ufo hovered over route 45 in mantua nj and turned on its side over the road and then flew sideways towards philadelphia pa. approximately 10 mph.I have never encountered any aircraft like this in my life. it made no noise and it seemed to have multicolored lights rotating inside one light. if anyone else witness this at approximately 9:40 pm on june 10th 2016
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Triangular ufo hovered over route 45 in mantua nj

content.detailedDescription:
Noticed from malta (cospicua) at 9:42 pm (local summer time)while observing night sky on roof : very bright silvery shining object round disc-shaped following a path from nw to e caught my eye. at first i thought it was a light from a low flying aircraft. its size was as much as 5 times the size and brightness of jupiter as visible from earth. spotted when at 70 degrees elevation from witness (approximately in the ursa major constellation) and disappeared at once as it reached an elevation of 40 degrees from witness to the east. its speed if at 40k feet from ground was as much as three times that of an aircraft traveling at 850<900 kms/hr at the same height. this fact excited me as i realised it was not an aircraft.
at 10:05pm and 10:12pm an orange point source was noticed first going from north to south at a constant elevation of 70<75 degrees and then back on the same track. estimated altitude was round 60<65k feet from ground. estimated speed over 2000 kms/hr. 
in all cases the witness checked real-time flight tracking/radar programmes on the web but none indicated any aircraft in the areas mentioned.
content.summary: Bright silver shining object - circa 5 times the size of visible jupiter

content.detailedDescription: Flying to coast.On june 12. 1115hrs. noted a single saucer shaped object above cloud horizon line at approx. 33,000 ft.The object stayed with jetliner for 10 minutes matching direction and speed and sight was lost as plane desended. photographs taken.Judging distance of 5-10 km. away.Pointed out to aircrew and fellow passengers.
content.summary: Flying home.Noted saucer with two tails 33,000 ft. above cloud horizon matching jet speed and direction..Lost sight as we defended.

content.detailedDescription:
2 observers: i was in my motor home when buddy who was outdoors knocked to advise odd unidentified aerial phenomenon. while collecting shoes and digging out digital camera, a portable radio plugged into cig lighter died. exiting, friend was 50 yards away in clearing looking upward. on way to join him i was distracted by brief conversation by 3rd party non observer in their car. asked if their car radio worked several times. by time they tested, it was working, some five minutes later. did not double check my radio but it was working by event end, and i would discover object had vanished while i was having that conversation; object possibly killing power while visible, or perhaps while changing state of being (ie, morphing, winking in or out of view, as would be witnessed.
...
as investigative writer and usaf ret. crash investigator, and frmr member/investigator nicap, mufon, apro, i 1st noted conditions. clear sunny weather with a single broad band of light whispy clouds at about 8k ft, some puffyness and clearing spots along the band. three object events would all take place along this band, each originating or first observed near to a vortext-like swirl opening in the cloud of almost identical size and visual. a fourth such swirl was seen in another, lesser band, but observation of any object that might be there not possible due to nearness to blinding sun. regardless the unusual similarity of the swirls and common nearness to uap deserves mention. this main cloud lay precisely along the descent portion of landing approach to pdx used by overseas and california pass jets, and was at the same altitude they would be at when there. parallel to the main cloud line was one chemtral quite nearby, and further away one contrail to the other side, both at 20k ft., jets long gone. contrails are thin and vanish in time starting at their end as if being erased, chemtrails just spread out bigger and bigger untill too thin to see as such. clouds, landing path ran n by ne. no aircraft or sounds of aircraft untill late in event, one heavy at 20k, one commuter jet at 5k, both flying due north and well away from sightings.
...
when joining friend he showed me where 1st object had been seen between opening in tree line along river, looking due south at about 30 degrees above horiz. described as orange spot that had seemed to slowly move east untill hidden by tree, that it was at times lost in thicker portions of cloud, no apparant chang in size. i knew where there was a better viewpoint in the treeline another 50 yards further within the trees. proceeding there, he remained in case visual reacquired. once relocated i scanned the site he indicated and saw nothing.
...
as he had indicated it moved eastward, scanned my view on assumption it might have sped up. just at eastern most portion of cloud along that path, just as concluding no object, the last thing i was looking at was a swirl. at that postion just then, almost adjacent, a white triangular shape twisted into existance in a fraction of a second. it then twisted more gently as a yellow rectangular shape appeared just as oddly at the lower portion of the triangle. my first impression was, mystery solved: sky divers, though at their apparant distance by size, i should have been able to see at least one man, none visible. it was also odd that they both remained in their associated relationship as if adjoined. but as they at first seemed to descend, i started to return to my friend with such explanation. i glanced back just before leaving useful vantage and noted that the 'chutes' were not descending, but smaller - as if traveling south instead of descending. the triangle had vanished, and seconds later the yellow part was swallowed by the cloud. remarkable updraft, i reasoned. calculated object to be over west linn when 1st seen, at about 1000 feet, if chutes. but given cloud interactions and cloud altitude, later realised too large to be chutes.
...
rejoining my friend, i offered the skydiver accounting only to find he was looking at yet another object just acquired. in the same cloud band both north and east of my observation was an orange rectangle of the same aspect ratio as the yellow 'chute'. however, it was much smaller and seemed well above the clouds. there was visible a small dark dot low and centered appropriately to be a sky diver, and i thought it seemed to rotate a bit as if steered or blown like a chute. however, my friend refuted the notion, noting it was getting smaller and smaller; it was ascending, not descending. indeed this was slowly happening, with possibly a slight westward. we both lost it at the same time: it may bave winked out or,by then, simply have been too small to well track with our eyes and reacquire.
...
1st object visible as small spot at same angle of view as second larger object/object pair. if like objects as presumed by common shape/color band, 2nd object was closer and lower than first. third object almost overhead, slightly east of us. though 2nd and 3rd events had attributes of chutes, they could not defy gravity as seen. the second observance indicates a fairly large size of several hundred feet and an ability to wink in and morph. however, the space between observances in time leaves open the possibility only one object was seen winking in and out at multiple locations. the proximity of near identical cloud swirls would seem to tie to winking in, and all would seem to have climbed in altitude and or flown slowly in different directions, 1st east, 2nd south, 3rd west.
... 
three attempts were made to photograph 3rd object w zoom while in blue sky, but though visible in viewfinder, image captured only sky and cloud.
content.summary: One object vanishing reappearing or three sequentially appearing along common line, each on different course.

content.detailedDescription:
These craft were disc shaped, one had a bell like dome on top of it,they had windows around the outside and had a dimly lit orange light on the top of it. 
i'd woken up in the middle of the night with the impulse to look out of the window, which i did. i saw all these craft hovering over the houses and witnessed a neighbours abduction. i live in the city so the houses are very close together and it's densely populated. one craft pulled up to the neighbours conservatory and seemed to unsteadily tilt to one side (i was later told by the et's that this was the result of a faulty rotational balance in the craft). it hovered over their conservatory for only a few minutes before the craft lit up in a bright, white light and disappeared out of our reality in the blink of an eye, taking my neighbour with them. then, another craft approached my house and i was telepathically instructed "hazel, go back to bed we're coming for you next."

i seemed to have no control over this and felt compelled to get back into bed and fall instantly asleep. the next thing i remember is them coming into my room through the walls. the room looked as though it was folding away and made of cardboard. i was completely paralyzed and unable to move, i tried to scream but i couldn't use my vocals either, i could just about squint my eyes open to see that the room was disappearing around me and the beings approaching me.

i then have memory loss after that point.
content.summary: Approx 3 or 4 close range craft hovering over houses in densely populated area carrying out abductions.

content.detailedDescription: I posted on here before about when my friend and i were at my pool and saw a ufo  circle us 3 times, and last night i was with my sister who is a skeptic, it was around 11pm and we were having a late night swim. she was swimming laps and i was floating on my back looking at the stars, there are a lot of lights in my area so you can't see a crystal clear sky. but i noticed something flying at a rapid rate directly above my pool, and it was almost like it was stirring up the water. i tried to show my sister but she didn't see it, i was very upset because she thought i just saw a bird. however, it appeared to have made a large circle and was passing over us again, this time slightly closer. you could see the lights, and it looked like a very fat v. my sister saw it this time, and since i'm a huge ufo finatic i was really excited and got out of the water. we lost sight of it, and saw it once more before we left. the ufo was a very dull color, but keep in mind it was night, and there were yellow lights on it.It was most certainly not a plaine or a bird. i thought it was strange though, i believe that was the exact same ufo i saw with my friend a few years ago. my family and i have witnessed many ufo sightings, the weirdest one was a ufo we saw in wa on vacation, it was the size of a 15 passenger van except circular and jet black, hovering about 10 ft over a n apple orchard. i would love to be a ufologist one day, they absolutely fascinate me. anyways, i hope this story helps someone understand if they've seen something strange.
content.summary: Triangle shaped ufo spotted for the second time in the same area, circled pool 3 times

content.detailedDescription: I went outside to smoke. while there a was looking at the moon with a star next to it when a bright light just appeared. when i say appeared i mean like it came from above and stopped. it moved a matter of feet (across the sky in my view) and then shot out to space. when i say shot i mean from a penny size to nothing in 2 seconds. this is the third sighting for me in the last year and a half. since i have to smoke outside and i'm always looking up. i'm beginning to think i'm being stalked.
content.summary: Light that went into space in 2 to 3 seconds

content.detailedDescription: On friday the 10th june 2016, stood in my back garden having a cigarette before going to bed, the sky was really over cast and no sky/stars observable, just the clouds, very dark. to the west in the direction of lichfield city i could see a really bright white star shining straight through the clouds, i instantly thought "bloody hell that's bright" and continued to watch, after about 6-7seconds it then changed colour and size, it went from bright white to a deep flame coloured orange and went to a rather large ball, at first i thought a star had exploded, however this wasn't in space, it was obvious at that point that whatever this was, it was inside the clouds, it lit up the inside of the cloud and i could see all the detail of the inner cloud, however the ball didn't move, flicker, make any further alterations at all. it stayed dead still while the cloud it was in continued to move at the normal air speed, after 10seconds or so it just went out and nothing further was seen.
content.summary: Bright star changed to large glowing orange ball

content.detailedDescription: Unknowingly at work 2 hours early. don't remember how i woke up. i had set 2 cell phones to alarm at different times between 3:30 am and 4 am each with no less than 4 alarms. i went to bed at 1:30 am, i believe that i woke up at about 2:30am to what i thought was the alarms for 3:30am. got to work with no one there. called boss who thought i was crazy. as the morning progressed the phones began changing to regular time in rapid speed. i only know this because when i finally figured out that i needed to see what time it really was that's when i noticed the time moving on both phones . i'm not sure what happened i'm still trying to figure out how i woke up because there's no way the alarms were ringing. and how do 2 separate phones from two different companies change time backwards at the same time???????
content.summary: Woke up 1 1/2 hours early unknowingly don't remember how i was awaken. unknowingly at work 2 hours early 2 cell phones 2 hours behind returning back to time quickly. went to bed at 1:30 am and up i guess at 2:30 am???

content.detailedDescription: At night my aunt and i set outside and enjoy nature, but this night we both looked towards the north and notice how low these two bright lights were and talked about how low it was and how close the lights were. it was like head lights but real close together. then i was saying how it looked like the lights were headed straight towards us. she reached over to get a cigarette and i turned to look at her then turned to continue to look at the lights and they were gone. we were both shocked that we could not fine them at all. i looked all around thinking maybe it was a plane and i could see the blinking lights on the plane and nothing. then i thought... i would soon hear the plane fly over us and there was nothing. we looked every where for a plane. there was no lights and no sound. it was like those lights disappeared. we have set there many times and watched planes fly by us from kansas city. we know exactly what they do. this was no airplane and it was gone in a flash. we looked everywhere in the sky for it. then tonight june 12th. i watched a light move from north to south and it just slowly disappeared in the sky. still no flashing lights and no sound of airplane. i dont know what it was, but thought i would tell you what i saw, so if anyone else seen it, you would have something to compare to.  both times they were there one second and then both left with no sign of anything.
content.summary: Looked like two real close bright head lights flying right at us. i thought that it was a airplane flying real low right at us. then i turned for a second to see what my aunt was doing and turned back and the bright head lights were gone.

content.detailedDescription:
This morning to get away from all the bad & horrid news being reported , decided to view the space on nasa's live stream , on the second camera  it was night night time shown but noticed on the lower left side of the screen a changing ufo so decided to continue to watch if the signal stays or not and if any more ufos will show up . 
soon the fast flashes begun going around the screen very quickly , most at first were coming from the left side shooting upwards across the screen , some then even appeared in the middle of the screen , again most went upwards , later on larger ufos flashed brightly zooming by ascending or going across , it was awesome :) 
in the approximate time i've counted 18 ufos that i could see go by in front of the iss .
i've tried my best to take screenshots but because of the speed of how they tend to move in space 
i didn't get all of them , then again some i did caught but noticed them later on when reviewing the these screenshots . 
when i left the site 1 main ufo remained on the screen . total time of watching was about 12 min.
content.summary: About !8 ufos in front of iss in space within 12 min of watching the live stream
